{"title":"Antiarritmicos-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neurología/Antiarritmicos-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Antiarritmicos","guid":"ePrFiFd4ZzB2eXpbvJ4W_w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Clase I\\N(Bloqueadores canales Na⁺)","guid":"lqhPSNEYl8hn8xjzPMnJpg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"IA","guid":"65aEjAewH96-xLQY4V-71Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Mecanismo: Bloqueo moderado canales Na⁺, prolongan duración del PA y período refractario efectivo (PRE).","guid":"Ic7nNqWePZBPfE6amiJMmg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Ejemplos: Quinidina, Procainamida, Disopiramida.","guid":"VGYLjDS4QNHytVz5hUC0BQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Uso: TPSV, FA, aleteo auricular, arritmias ventriculares.","guid":"44vYu9ImX9ZP3TQrTadIWA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"EA: Prolongación QT → TdP, lupus inducido por fármacos (procainamida), IC (disopiramida).","guid":"QdK_pPDsOsqdsAx5zfdQPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"IB","guid":"yVO5XzOXV2v8Lrr-97RIRw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Mecanismo: Bloqueo débil Na⁺, acortan duración PA.","guid":"bcPhPhcn39i48J2poEi8PA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Ejemplos: Lidocaína, Mexiletina.","guid":"UV4GEPT6j_DJYJwvmUqqXw","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Uso: Arritmias ventriculares post-IAM, intoxicación digital.","guid":"JlsqKtMCoIpDZ4cTMPsbGA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"EA: Mareos, convulsiones, bloqueo AV, extrasístoles ventriculares.","guid":"Nu09WAK4jYu_fBczLgNZaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"IC","guid":"Mt5RuZLW91oWf1-_L9Hwrg","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Mecanismo: Bloqueo fuerte Na⁺, sin efecto en PA.","guid":"lUnpjUSrOr8sU8xCIoLoqA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Ejemplos: Flecainida, Propafenona.","guid":"6y5mAx9TRuVoaVSOJdVB8g","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Uso: FA, aleteo auricular, arritmias refractarias.","guid":"iQY4m326OVl8_t9VABznpg","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"EA: Proarritmias, contraindicado post-IAM.","guid":"TVvm7_1PBeLidnnTU5IOfA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Clase II\\N(β-bloqueadores)","guid":"180QAf0nxwU-MRQ2Bnr7-Q","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Mecanismo: Inhiben adenilato ciclasa → ↓ AMPc → ↓ Ca²⁺ intracelular → ↓ FC y conducción AV.","guid":"hcKhvkCJ7Hh1sHIX9yqYbQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Ejemplos: Metoprolol, Esmolol, Propanolol.","guid":"5kripJM1tq1CkSfbJvrm6A","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"Uso: FA (control frecuencia), TPSV, arritmias ventriculares.","guid":"OjmjDrYifF-snvYslKATbw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"EA: Bloqueo AV, bradicardia, IC, broncoespasmo.","guid":"PzAlSsYPd6jcG0Iyp7RXKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Clase III\\N(Bloqueadores canales K⁺)","guid":"7uDtXdZxcBmrRDumuKbhfQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Mecanismo: Inhiben corrientes K⁺, prolongan PA y QT.","guid":"rgJ-CgJKtyumnyYezrM_7Q","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Ejemplos: Amiodarona, Sotalol, Dronedarona.","guid":"hHO4VrKl4SrCNVCDI0rCHA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Uso: FA (control ritmo), arritmias ventriculares.","guid":"131UysDXKu4l1tkomEFAeQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"EA: Prolongación QT → TdP, fibrosis pulmonar, disfunción tiroidea (amiodarona).","guid":"qOuYCIejtMKFEfgoJl_gEQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Clase IV\\N(Bloqueadores canales Ca²⁺)","guid":"tl1MpSqMt6rR017i4N34ZQ","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Mecanismo: Inhiben canales Ca²⁺, ↓ velocidad conducción AV, prolongan PRE.","guid":"WU1DB8Ul0vALfXjxfx3B-Q","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Ejemplos: Verapamilo, Diltiazem.","guid":"Bo4JsaLodmV0HB1x-33zRw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Uso: FA (control frecuencia), TPSV.","guid":"TvlKunQ6_eTrORCRphzakQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"EA: Bloqueo AV, bradicardia, IC, estreñimiento.","guid":"vxFvDMGYt2s5f5wKrtxkoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Clase V (Otros\\Nmecanismos)","guid":"b0OgFBvYHGCUmXAClp3iyg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Adenosina","guid":"Sm7sPojh-vndtcTJ6NPDsg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Mecanismo: Activa proteína Gi → ↓ adenilato ciclasa → ↓ AMPc → inactiva canales Ca²⁺ tipo L y activa canales K⁺\\N→ ↓ Ca²⁺ intracelular y ↑ eflujo de K⁺ → hiperpolarización → bloqueo transitorio nodo AV (acción corta ∼ 15 seg).","guid":"N02htqc6oVDL7I4WtvYtWg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"Ypjkwn0Ftx_VceN9YxnPtg","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"◦ TPSV (diagnóstico y terminación)","guid":"j_UaJiv1fAQMVJ_Z8UMXeg","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"◦ Diagnóstico de FA en taquiarritmias supraventriculares","guid":"y6qKRWNLxWb2FkTgkNyirQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"◦ Prueba de esfuerzo farmacológica en cintigrafía de perfusión miocárdica","guid":"bWJsObWFPECNiID8AgJ1NA","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"33","text":"Administración: Bolo IV rápido (vida media < 10 seg), dosis repetidas si es necesario.","guid":"6q4PMz6efxM3wA64M_Pfcw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"33","text":"EA: Dolor torácico, rubor, hipotensión, broncoespasmo, sensación de muerte inminente, bloqueo AV, asistolia.","guid":"k-3x4r-JJUriYiR-yIFIPQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"33","text":"Contraindicaciones: Síndromes de pre-excitación (antidrómico, WPW), bloqueo AV, asma.","guid":"bWYDtiakBuV4k8K2KKAjgA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"33","text":"Interacciones: Teofilina y cafeína ↓ efecto (antagonistas de receptores de adenosina).","guid":"Ii7Jovxyzbk8SGk8a5C1xQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"32","text":"Digoxina","guid":"0jZzIZ1bdFsKmsNfAozcGA","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Mecanismo: Inhibe Na⁺/K⁺-ATPasa → ↑ Na⁺ intracelular → ↓ eficacia del intercambiador Na⁺/Ca²⁺ → ↑ Ca²⁺ intracelular → ↑ contractilidad, ↓ FC.","guid":"WJbWj61vnEq5tHSXEtLFJw","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Indicaciones: FA, aleteo auricular, IC sistólica crónica.","guid":"e8IT6-LpPZAiTgDl5YXaAg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"EA: Visión amarilla, náuseas, arritmias.","guid":"TuRDHNR0VWOI6wajXZNuTA","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"EA: Ver \"Intoxicación por glucósidos cardíacos\".","guid":"X9K_Teun0UcxH7sAr-0zZQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"32","text":"Sulfato de\\NMagnesio","guid":"lDRdG_DP90BORZbuCoc7bw","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Mecanismo: ↓ entrada de Ca²⁺ → previene postdespolarizaciones tempranas (PDE).","guid":"kuvxfBrHaPTT3pXcsI62Dw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"_mbWPMnvSpBOaaVEB1IZGA","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"◦ TdP","guid":"BX1ZhNSe9CLtVuWRZyr1zA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"◦ Taquiarritmias ventriculares refractarias (p.ej., TV polimórfica)","guid":"H-J0UJX9TSFbLr4nownxJA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"◦ Intoxicación por digoxina","guid":"wC7diSB3Uub_vLaWcVIpBg","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"◦ Eclampsia, constipación, tocolisis","guid":"OmGRS-gAtosyTfn3bnNA3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"EA: Hipotensión, asistolia, somnolencia, rubor, pérdida de reflejos, depresión respiratoria.","guid":"ZYtq0H2ZarJlM6Pf7yhkFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"32","text":"Ivabradina","guid":"BRVXUkZtHYpi4H6w2Hl6Bw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Mecanismo: Inhibe selectivamente canal If en células marcapasos del nodo SA → prolonga despolarización lenta (fase 4) → ↓ FC.","guid":"eEIG1sjRhcEDr2zbgUcRYw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Indicaciones: Enfermedad coronaria estable sintomática, IC crónica (NYHA II-IV) en pacientes intolerantes a β-bloqueadores.","guid":"lcQhp48OqU6Jh5RcPrORWw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"EA: Fenómenos luminosos (↑ brillo visual), bradicardia, hipertensión.","guid":"w09MF6eWsKuX2vuXu3trXg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":59,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Antiarritmicos-2024","id":"map_1386","resolved_references":[]}